<title>
Ignition Coil (Plug Cap) Inspection
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove ignition coil assemblies. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70B1806003"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Check ignition coil assembly for damage, deterioration and terminal corrosion.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
If defective condition is found, replace ignition coil assembly.
</ptxt>
</s1>
